{"tid":213870,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"15分鐘煮濃茄意粉","createTime":"2017-04-23T11:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T12:23:21.000Z","uid":106936,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81cb67271201e4bac694b93742bddfd9ba9fa7bc","tid":213870,"uid":106936,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T11:55:11.000Z","msg":"材料:<br />\n意粉-- 適量,圖片為一人份<br />\n茄膏--一舊, 如果冇 可以用茄汁,大約用三~四包<br />\n水-- 煮意粉(蓋過意粉), 開茄膏(約150ml)<br />\n鹽-- 1/2茶匙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Uz39j0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Uz39j0.jpg&h=e3083e73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先煲水,水滾 落鹽落意粉,煮約7分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXfAMB0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXfAMB0.jpg&h=bf13f9dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n意粉煮完裝起備用.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZqzFi2n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZqzFi2n.jpg&h=df34cf81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為一人份,茄膏用一粒. 我用依隻,之前係日本買番黎未試過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S8N11J5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS8N11J5.jpg&h=62b8a968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n煮滾150ml水再加入茄膏煮融<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Fyz2OP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Fyz2OP.jpg&h=020447c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等茄醬開始收汁,熄火將意粉同醬汁撈勻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hsjCVp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hsjCVp.jpg&h=3df48e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上碟,食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f65c298d1d62e101e108e33e2945e29ace012bb","tid":213870,"uid":94935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T11:58:55.000Z","msg":"乜配料都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b58eb2a29038655225736b92627c41f06863e1","tid":213870,"uid":106936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:02:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜配料都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n速煮速食所以冇加<br />\n如果加可以係煮汁個陣加免治牛/豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"154a20c642a740e1fb7495509bccf74cc274905d","tid":213870,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:04:11.000Z","msg":"加隻煎蛋都好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b458217e0131c2dd8a8bdaef1d60ba6e1609615f","tid":213870,"uid":35069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:04:17.000Z","msg":"15分鐘乜撚配料都斬倒落去啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa7ff4ec0ad06b25dbbb43b86af83d46929daf2","tid":213870,"uid":88650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:06:23.000Z","msg":"做乜個茄膏咁似咖喱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78066964b2d9c675565313580a2ce817eaf6530","tid":213870,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:06:31.000Z","msg":"黑椒汁咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b222eedf0d4008becf581fb62f5041812821887","tid":213870,"uid":106936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:06:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做乜個茄膏咁似咖喱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為係熟茄掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b19fe8acc6c9fa010c7dc7bc543c451b920d97f","tid":213870,"uid":106936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:07:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>15分鐘乜撚配料都斬倒落去啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係加唔加嘅問題,係有冇嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62880e5e522073a0896bc453c9e4dfe772b2f4ef","tid":213870,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:12:16.000Z","msg":"我今晚都係煮意粉，都係十五分鐘你望下我個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7936df9647a412a6b95b7118549b3d986f70f9","tid":213870,"uid":106936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:13:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黑椒汁咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n特色黎應該係,夠濃,好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee53de08312da228b135492743a12e2df64549b","tid":213870,"uid":106936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:15:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我今晚都係煮意粉，都係十五分鐘你望下我個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哪有shell<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企有咩就煮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff3fbd67cf409721b6af60c3fd4d72723672b9a1","tid":213870,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:17:59.000Z","msg":"俾狗食都要配料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}